## üìä Status Meanings

- üü¢ **Active** - In Master Plan, ready to implement
- üü° **In Progress** - Currently being implemented
- ‚úÖ **Complete** - Finished, kept for reference
- ‚è∏Ô∏è **Paused** - Temporarily halted (not in execution sequence)
- üìã **Reference** - Guide only, not in Master Plan
- ‚ùå **Deprecated** - No longer relevant

---

**Remember: Master Plan is THE execution plan. All other plans are reference guides. Keep Master Plan current. Reference it always.**

